# State view GUI - includes terrain photo icon widgets (3 of 3 terrain files)
# Each iconType auto-shows when the matching province modifier is present.
# Terrain photos are applied via add_province_modifier in history/states/ files.
#
# © Millenium Dawn 2016-2025

